{"id": 1915, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你都会通过哪些小事找自我认同？", "description": "决定你是啥样人的一些小细节是啥？我们列出了一些普遍选项，找不到可选的请在评论区补充说明。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 14233, "comment_count": 36, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170918183029b5JdEGPYe9K7AHxc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-20T17:00:02Z", "questions": [{"id": 3002, "title": "现如今你都会通过哪些小事找自我认同？", "content": "现如今你都会通过哪些小事找自我认同？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 236402, "content": "通过喜欢的球队确认自己是哪一种体系/打法爱好者", "image": "img/option/option/2017091909285615ILvzQtdAgVeBb8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236504, "content": "通过喜欢的二次元人物/偶像确认自己的理想型", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093041sHSLTu91kUqlcFev.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236506, "content": "看选秀节目站队，比如是Gai粉还是PGone粉", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093349c3VeqxFwlh0jNPIi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236507, "content": "根据钟爱的影视剧类型，发现自己某些隐蔽的性格特质", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093112ZMU7zB6FtAKQj5GT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236508, "content": "打游戏的风格，爱担任肉盾/输出/奶，喜欢主动出击/偷袭反击", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093125Tkt1FKOzuGAPn5iX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236509, "content": "不喜欢/喜欢某个演艺明星，确认自己认为糟糕/优秀的特质是啥", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093140qClkKnxNLuevIhH8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236510, "content": "不喜欢/喜欢某个作家、艺术家等，确认自己喜欢的艺术手法和理念", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093204KalYxoMvGB3wT2Qf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236511, "content": "看诸如初老症、拖延症之类的现代病描述，对号入座", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093221SBuAJMY0xCOZijnw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236513, "content": "MBTI十六型人格分类/五大性格特质等性格理论分析", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093232HkZ5qpauOc7yzf9D.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236514, "content": "星座，也不怎么信，但好奇自己的星座是怎么被描述的", "image": "img/option/option/20170919093246xIlcQ5uXWAj8km1r.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236522, "content": "看到不认同的评论，边想怎么反驳边完善自己的观点", "image": "img/option/option/201709191000273MWYp8KZPHloR9Cm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}